Event Sources
 ├─ Contributor signup (web/app)
 ├─ Storefront checkout (Shopify bundles)
 ├─ GitHub commits & workflows (Pages, Sitemap, Theme Sync)
 ├─ OracleSignal notifications (GitHub → OracleSignal)
 └─ Scheduled jobs (Crypto Oracle 24‑Hour Loop)

Core Pipelines
 1) Onboarding (Atomic Drop)
    → POST /onboarding/init
    → GET /credit-status/{id}
    → IF freeze/fraud → POST /fraud-alert-verify
    → PUT /audit-log/onboarding
    → PUSH → Dashboard: compliance feed
    → POST /legacy/broadcast (snapshot)

 2) Storefront Transactions
    → POST /storefront/transaction
    → GET /dispute-log/{id}
    → IF dispute → FLAG + require review
    → PUT /audit-log/transaction
    → PUSH → Dashboard: order + compliance status
    → POST /legacy/broadcast (order proof)

 3) Signal Routing (GitHub → OracleSignal)
    → GitHub commit event
    → Normalize → repo/workflow/runId
    → POST /signal/github/commit
    → PUT /audit-log/signal
    → PUSH → Dashboard: signal stream
    → POST /legacy/broadcast (signal digest)

 4) Deploys (Static Content, Pages, Shopify Theme)
    → Build artifact
    → Validate checksum + integrity
    → Publish → CDN/Pages/Shopify
    → PUT /audit-log/deploy
    → PUSH → Dashboard: release notes
    → POST /legacy/broadcast (release manifest)

 5) Sitemap & Indexing
    → Workflow run
    → Generate sitemap.xml + robots.txt
    → Validate endpoints
    → Publish → Pages
    → PUT /audit-log/sitemap
    → PUSH → Dashboard: SEO status

 6) Crypto Oracle Loop
    → Scheduled trigger
    → Fetch market data
    → Analyze signals
    → POST /signal/crypto
    → PUT /audit-log/crypto
    → PUSH → Dashboard: oracle feed
    → IF failure → POST /incident/create + notify
